---
title: Tomato and Mozzarella Risotto with fresh basil and chilli
description: Risotto is a classic Italian dish consisting of rice that's slowly cooked with stock until it's rich and creamy. This particular one is of the veggie variety and features juicy tomatoes and fresh chilli for optional added bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF220930_R10_W47_IE_IEXVCLV0079-1_MB_Main_6_high-fac968d3.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/tomato-and-mozzarella-risotto-6345606b2c641ef47c489f3a-b5675f52.pdf
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
